{"tid":794123,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山神搏老命加操　鬥熱刺有望復出","createTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T05:09:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d718897bd141aea45130c1fa0ac3935a004a20d","tid":794123,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"曼聯周一會在英超主場迎戰熱刺，屆時紅魔鬼有可能有智利國腳前鋒阿歷斯山齊士傷癒，趕及在這場大戰中復出。<br />\n<br />\n山神上周末因為受傷的關係，缺席了曼聯作客2:3不敵白禮頓的賽事，紅魔鬼領隊摩連奴當時表示，阿歷斯山齊士不會傷出多於兩星期。不過，根據山神在個人Instagram接連上載的影片，他有可能在短時間內就能夠復出。這位智利國腳所上載的影片當中，其一可見他身穿整齊曼聯練習球衣，並寫上「為儘快復出而練習，曼聯加油！」。未幾，山神又再上載自己在家附近和愛犬一同跑步的影片。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯開季踢了兩場聯賽，暫時取得一勝一負，以兩戰得3分暫時排在聯賽榜第9位。"},{"pid":"3612ee461c35bb563aa0fcfc620ec054653e8170","tid":794123,"uid":124020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全能到 pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿傾想入幾多球啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d9b297377d5461797ce0891f955d610a178646","tid":794123,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"神魔合一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf18d7896c7b091ef6261e84b00421d183da174","tid":794123,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃<i